<div type="content">
<ab>Gnedige fraw, wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> wie Hanns
                                                  <expan>Öpfenhaws<ex>er</ex></expan>, der uns und
                                                die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on schuld und on
                                                sach etwieoft beschedigt und gerawbt hat, zu Kalb zu
                                                fenknuss <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> sey.
                                                  <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> wir
                                                  <expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> Göldlein,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, zu
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> und im befolhen
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit
                                                  <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> zu reden.
                                                  <expan>Bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr gnade mit
                                                  <expan>ganze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiss, was
                                                  <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> zu disem mal in
                                                  <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> von
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewr gnade
                                                  <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan>, daz ir in darinn
                                                  <expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> verhörn, im des
                                                  <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gelawben und uns
                                                ewr gnade und <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
                                                darinn
                                                  <add><expan>günstiklich<ex>en</ex></expan></add>
<expan>beweis<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet. Als etc.
                                                Das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
